Configure Username and Email: 
  --> git config --global user.name = "Your Name"
  --> git config --global user.email = "example@gmail.com"

Cloning Repository:
  --> git clone https://url/of/repository
  --> cd repository

Create a Brach
  --> git checkout -b <branch_name>

Staging Changes:
  for All files:
    --> git add .
  for specific fies:
    --> git add file1 file2 ...
Commit the changes:
  --> git commit -m "your commit string"


Push the changes into branch:
  --> git push origin <new-branch> or <Existing branch>


Pull the code from another branch
  --> git pull origin <name-branch>
